  "title": "Service Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Perform general servicing of aircon systems</li></ul><ul><li>Install, Maintain and Repair Industrial Air Filtration Plants, ACMV, HVAC Systems and Air Ventilation Systems.</li></ul><ul><li>Submit daily and weekly reports to the direct manager</li></ul><ul><li><p>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the Superiors</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Meticulous, hardworking and willing to learn</li><li>Good team player and able to work independently</li><li>More than 3 years relevant working experience</li><li>Possess Class 3 driving license</li><li>May require to work on weekend & overtime</li><li>Singaporeans are most welcome to apply</li></ul>",
